OL,6,FA teacher has been forced to give up
OL,7,Fwork to care for her three-year-old
OL,8,Fdaughter with additional learning
OL,9,Fneeds because there's no room for her
OL,10,Fin their local special school.
OL,12,FRebecca Davies, mum to Maggie and
OL,13,FMillie, has paused her 10-year
OL,14,Fteaching career indefinitely because
OL,15,Fof what she says is a lack of support
OL,16,Ffor parents of children with
OL,17,FAdditional Learning Needs (ALN).
