OL,6,FDaughter Millie, who turns four this
OL,7,Fyear, is autistic and has global
OL,8,Fdevelopmental delay and severe
OL,9,Flearning difficulties.
OL,11,F"She's lush, she's gorgeous," her mum
OL,12,Fsays.
OL,14,F"She's the most loving little girl.
OL,15,FShe's cheeky. She loves a thrill.
OL,16,FShe's absolutely brilliant."
