OL,3,CMum forced to give up career as school
OL,4,Chas no room for her autistic daughter
OL,6,FMillie technically has a place at
OL,7,FYsgol Heol Goffa, a school in Llanelli
OL,8,Ffor children with complex needs, but
OL,9,Fhas no start date because the school
OL,10,Fhas no more room.
OL,12,FRebecca says the process of trying to
OL,13,Fget the appropriate education
OL,14,Fprovision for her daughter has been
OL,15,F"horrendous" and "heartbreaking".
OL,17,FThe teacher is among a number of
OL,18,Ffamilies speaking to ITV News about
OL,19,Fthe challenges they face in securing
OL,20,Fthe best for their children with ALN,
OL,21,Fwhich you can read more about here.
