OL,3,CMum forced to give up career as school
OL,4,Chas no room for her autistic daughter
OL,6,F"I've had to finish my career, a 10-
OL,7,Fyear teaching career, because there is
OL,8,Fno support," Rebecca told ITV Cymru
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,F"Until you're in the situation it's
OL,12,Fimpossible to understand. My children
OL,13,Fcome before everything, but it's been
OL,14,Fhorrendous.
OL,16,F"I feel Millie's not valued like other
OL,17,Fchildren and that's heartbreaking as a
OL,18,Fparent. I've got one neurotypical
OL,19,Fchild who's thriving in a Welsh
OL,20,Fmainstream school, and I've got Millie
OL,21,Fwho is waiting.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
