OL,6,F"In the meantime, while we are waiting
OL,7,Ffor Millie to get her place, what
OL,8,Fhappens then? What intervention
OL,9,Fhappens?
OL,11,F"There's no real support in the
OL,12,Fmeantime for how you to help her
OL,13,Fprogress.
OL,15,F"You're kind of just left to it.
OL,17,F"Meanwhile, every other child has the
OL,18,Fopportunity for school, socialisation,
OL,19,Feducation, and Millie's at home. She's
OL,20,Fgot nowhere to go.
