OL,6,F"The educational panel have said the
OL,7,Fbest place for Millie educationally is
OL,8,Fa severe learning difficulty school,
OL,9,Fwhich is Heol Goffa. There's no room
OL,10,Ffor her.
OL,12,F"There's capacity for 74, there's
OL,13,Falready 124 children in the school, so
OL,14,Fthere's no room.
OL,16,F"We're just waiting. There's no place
OL,17,Ffor her. They can't tell me how long
OL,18,Fthey're going to be.
