OL,6,F"It's a game of just waiting and
OL,7,Fhoping and doing as much as you can at
OL,8,Fhome and persevering."
OL,10,FRebecca is among many parents who were
OL,11,Fshocked when Carmarthenshire Council
OL,12,Fscrapped plans to build a larger,
OL,13,Freplacement school due to budget
OL,14,Fconstraints.
OL,16,F"Getting Millie into Ysgol Heol Goffa
OL,17,Fwas a battle in itself. I pushed for
OL,18,Fit strongly because of what an amazing
OL,19,Fschool it is. What goes on in there is
OL,20,Fphenomenal.
