OL,6,FCarmarthenshire Council said in a
OL,7,Fstatement that a review of the current
OL,8,FALN specialist provision in Llanelli
OL,9,Fwill begin in the autumn.
OL,11,FCouncil leader Darren Price said
OL,12,Fearlier this month: "I appreciate the
OL,13,Flast few months have been difficult,
OL,14,Fsince the decision was taken in May
OL,15,Fnot to continue with the plans to
OL,16,Fbuild a new special school due to
OL,17,Fsignificantly increased costs.
